name: POAntibacterials
title: PO Antibacterials
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for PO antibacterial medications for use in the treatment of infections of suspected bacterial origin or sepsis),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Medication),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes PO forms of antibacterial which may be given by mouth (orally) or given by any enteral route, for example via nasogastric tube),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes injectable (IV, IM) forms of antibacterial medications)
